It depends on whether the disability is work related or not. If work related usually 1 year. If not work related, if you qualify under family medical leave act, then you can take up to 12 weeks. To qualify, there has to be a minimum of 50 employees, you have worked there for a year, and have been full time.t depends on whether the disability is work related or not. If work related usually 1 year. If not work related, if you qualify under family medical leave act, then you can take up to 12 weeks. To qualify, there has to be a minimum of 50 employees, you have worked there for a year, and have been full time.
